  <Lines>k__BackingField:
  - 'You were once among the greatest wizards alive...

    Then a forbidden spell
    tore the Words of magic from your mind.'
  - 'Now you wake in a strange, living world with only fragments of your power left.

    The
    Words that shaped your spells are scattered, buried, and guarded.'
  - Gather what you can. Craft, survive, and push beyond the safety of the first
    lands, where stronger enemies and rarer secrets wait.
  - Recover the lost Words, rebuild your magic, and uncover who dared to erase you.
